560w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 827px) 100vw, 827px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 827px) 100vw, 827px\" srcset=\"/static/fa597e81573701bd4750dc422cc012cb/0c2b8/television-polls-scaled-1.jpg 207w,\n/static/fa597e81573701bd4750dc422cc012cb/0dbe3/television-polls-scaled-1.jpg 414w,\n/static/fa597e81573701bd4750dc422cc012cb/deba3/television-polls-scaled-1.jpg 827w,\n/static/fa597e81573701bd4750dc422cc012cb/35099/television-polls-scaled-1.jpg 1241w,\n/static/fa597e81573701bd4750dc422cc012cb/7f9aa/television-polls-scaled-1.jpg 1654w,\n/static/fa597e81573701bd4750dc422cc012cb/bb9a8/television-polls-scaled-1.jpg 2560w\" src=\"/static/fa597e81573701bd4750dc422cc012cb/deba3/television-polls-scaled-1.jpg\" alt=\"Photo by JESHOOTS.com from Pexels\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nDespite numerous stories about the death of traditional television viewership, a recent online survey by <a href=\"http://www.msn.com\">MSN</a> revealed that 72% of the responding audience chose <i>Cable, Satellite or Traditional Television Viewership</i> amongst viewing options “they watch most at home”.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nOnly 19% of the 231,478 respondents chose Netflix and 2% chose Internet services like Sling.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nThese results were posted as of June 19, 2017.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nThe PM Group is the most dominant buyer of television in San Antonio and South Texas. If you need help deciphering the challenges facing advertisers in today’s volatile advertising market, give agency president Fran Yanity a call at 210-490-2554 and we’ll get your advertising costs down and your business generating more business!<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<strong><u><a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com\">About The PM Group</a>:</u></strong> The PM Group was founded in 1988. Over the past 30 years, the agency has continued to grow and is currently listed as San Antonio’s Largest Advertising Agency by the <em>San Antonio Business Journal</em>. The PM Group’s client roster spans numerous industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profit, real estate and fitness. In addition, the agency hosts an annual Charity Gala every February that to date has raised over $2.5 million for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations in the last 15 years!  It is our way of giving back to the community that we so humbly serve.</p>\n","title":"New MSN Poll Reveals TV Viewership is Still King!","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"New MSN Poll Reveals TV Viewership is Still King!","url":"/new-msn-poll-reveals-tv-viewership-still-king/"}],"title":"TV Viewership is King According to MSN Poll | The PM Group","metaDesc":"A new poll shows TV still dominating the competition for home viewership. Luckily, The PM Group is the most dominant TV buyer in San Antonio.","focuskw":"viewership","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"TV Viewership is King According to MSN Poll | The PM Group","opengraphDescription":"A new poll shows TV still dominating the competition for home viewership. Luckily, The PM Group is the most dominant TV buyer in San Antonio.","opengraphImage":{"altText":"","sourceUrl":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/television-polls-scaled-1.jpg","srcSet":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/television-polls-scaled-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/television-polls-scaled-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/television-polls-scaled-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/television-polls-scaled-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/television-polls-scaled-1-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https://thepmgroup